    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/muxialiang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1399787-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/muxialiang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">山下猫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-06-23"
      class="main-meta">2013-06-23 00:03:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6130691_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  终于在早晨公车中读完《观念》，在读中段的时评时，真的觉得这是刘瑜赚奶粉钱的书——平易近人、生动卖萌。但是里面缺点也很明显： 流于表面——《底线时分》把警察不殴打狱中的曼德拉归为“有底线”，而这个纯粹道德方面的结论会不会太表面太幼稚？在《我们在输出什么》一文她...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6130691/#comments">(11回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">80有用 / 7没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6130691_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6130691_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





